阿根廷[[前锋_(足球)|前锋]][[利昂内尔·梅西|利昂内尔·梅西]]与葡萄牙前锋[[克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多|克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多]]是当世最杰出的两位足球运动员，统治足坛长达十多年，被广泛称为绝代双骄。他们之间的竞争经常被媒体以及球迷称之为'''梅西C罗之争'''（{{lang-en|Messi–Ronaldo rivalry}}），简称'''梅罗之争'''或'''绝代双骄之争'''。他们二人总共赢得了12座[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]（梅西拥有7座，C罗拥有5座），以及合计10座[[欧洲金靴奖|欧洲金靴奖]]（梅西赢得6次，C罗赢得4次）。梅罗二人被球迷、媒体、记者、以及其他球员广泛认为是时代最佳球员以及历史最佳球员。他们也是在职业生涯中赢得了最多奖杯的两名足球运动员，至今合计赢得了66座奖杯（梅西赢得35座，C罗赢得31座）。他们都曾在一个赛季中打进超过50粒进球。梅西与C罗都名列在足球历史上{{le|打进超过500粒进球的足球运动员列表|List of footballers with 500 or more goals|打进了超过500粒正式比赛进球的51名球员名单}}中，但与名单上大部分人不同的是，他们都为自己的俱乐部以及国家队打进了超过700粒进球。

记者和权威人士经常争论两位球员的个人优点，以确定二者中谁才是足球历史中的最佳球员。无论个人喜好如何，媒体一致认为他们都是这个时代中最出色的球员，因为他们的表现已经远远超过了同龄人。梅西的盘带技巧可能是足球历史上最好的，而C罗在社交媒体上的影响力，在世界范围内都得到了广泛的赞赏。<ref>{{cite news |last=Smith |first=Ben |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17786045 |title=Barcelona's Messi v Real Madrid's Ronaldo |date=2012-04-20 |access-date=2014-10-13 |work=BBC |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905081616/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17786045 |archive-date=2012-09-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Rice |first=Simon |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/lionel-messi-v-cristiano-ronaldo--worlds-greatest-players-locked-in-new-battle-8567328.html |title=Lionel Messi v Cristiano Ronaldo – world's greatest players locked in new battle |date=2013-04-10 |access-date=2014-10-13 |work=[[独立报|独立报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028195727/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/european/lionel-messi-v-cristiano-ronaldo--worlds-greatest-players-locked-in-new-battle-8567328.html |archive-date=2014-10-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Mendes |first=Chris |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/10923614/World-Cup-2014-Cristiano-Ronaldos-personal-duel-with-Lionel-Messi-is-affecting-his-performances-for-Portugal.html |title=Cristiano Ronaldo's personal duel with Lionel Messi is affecting his performances for Portugal |date=2014-06-24 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007135938/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/10923614/World-Cup-2014-Cristiano-Ronaldos-personal-duel-with-Lionel-Messi-is-affecting-his-performances-for-Portugal.html |archive-date=2014-10-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Hughes |first=Rob |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/10/09/sports/soccer/09iht-soccer09.html |title=Messi and Ronaldo: 2 Stars in Their Own Universe |date=2012-10-08 |access-date=2014-11-19 |work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130220192523/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/10/09/sports/soccer/09iht-soccer09.html |archive-date=2013-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Marcotti |first=Gabriele|url=https://online.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424052702304724404577289380688703556 |title=The Phenomenon of Messi and Ronaldo |date=2012-03-18 |access-date=2014-11-19 |work=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]}}</ref>二人之间的竞争可以被其他运动中的两位佼佼者中的竞争来做比较，比如拳击运动中的[[穆罕默德·阿里|穆罕默德·阿里]]与[[乔·弗雷泽|乔·弗雷泽]]的竞争、网球运动中的[[费德勒与纳达尔对战史|罗杰·费德勒与拉斐尔·纳达尔]]的竞争和[[比约恩·博里|比约恩·博里]]与[[约翰·麦肯罗|约翰·麦肯罗]]的竞争、NBA「大鳥」[[拉里·伯德|拉里·伯德]]和「魔術師」[[魔術強森|魔術強森]]的競爭，以及[[一级方程式赛车|F1]]赛车运动中的[[阿兰·普罗斯特|阿兰·普罗斯特]]与[[艾尔顿·塞纳|艾尔顿·塞纳]]的竞争。<ref>{{cite news |last=Hunter |first=Graham |url=http://espn.go.com/sports/soccer/news/_/id/5842703/el-clasico-all-ronaldo-vs-messi |title=The game's best rivalry |date=2010-11-28 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=ESPN |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006150207/http://espn.go.com/sports/soccer/news/_/id/5842703/el-clasico-all-ronaldo-vs-messi |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Messi v Ronaldo |publisher=[[天空体育|天空体育]] |date=2011-10-17 |url=http://www.skysports.com/news/21227/7235124/messi-v-ronaldo |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006105413/http://www.skysports.com/news/21227/7235124/messi-v-ronaldo |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/opinion/leaders/article3637725.ece |title=The Special Two |date=2012-12-21 |access-date=2014-10-13 |work=[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]] |archive-date=2015-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626225332/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/opinion/leaders/article3637725.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref>一些评论员选择分析两者的技术打法以对比二人，<ref>{{cite news |last=Hughes |first=Rob |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/14/sports/soccer/14iht-soccer14.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |title=Ronaldo May Look Like the Best, but There Is Someone Better |date=2011-09-13 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006221154/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/14/sports/soccer/14iht-soccer14.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>而另外一部分的辩论则围绕着二者的精神属性展开：C罗经常被描述为更有性格的那个；而梅西则是更内向的那个，但也拥有一定的领导力。<ref>{{cite news |last=Hayward |first=Paul |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2009/may/26/cristiano-ronaldo-lionel-messi-champions-league |title=Cristiano Ronaldo versus Lionel Messi pits showman against shy man |date=2009-05-26 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009050509/http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2009/may/26/cristiano-ronaldo-lionel-messi-champions-league |archive-date=2014-10-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Lewis |first=Tim |url=https://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/2013/nov/24/cristiano-ronaldo-real-madrid-portugal-football |title=Cristiano Ronaldo: he's got a god-given talent – and he knows it |date=2013-11-24 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006163656/http://www.theguardian.com/theobserver/2013/nov/24/cristiano-ronaldo-real-madrid-portugal-football |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Calvin |first=Michael |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/the-last-word-crunch-time-for-lionel-messi-and-cristiano-ronaldo-9537924.html |title=Crunch time for Lionel Messi and Cristiano Ronaldo |date=2014-06-15 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[独立报|独立报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006094101/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/the-last-word-crunch-time-for-lionel-messi-and-cristiano-ronaldo-9537924.html |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Storey |first=Daniel |url=http://www1.skysports.com/FIFA-World-Cup-2014/news/15241/9350562/ronaldo-the-world8217s-best |title=Ronaldo: The world's best? |date=2014-06-16 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[天空体育|天空体育]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006071315/http://www1.skysports.com/FIFA-World-Cup-2014/news/15241/9350562/ronaldo-the-world8217s-best |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>

俱乐部层面，梅西与C罗为西班牙两大豪门（同样也是死敌）[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]以及[[皇家马德里足球俱乐部|皇家马德里]]效力近十载。自C罗在2009年加盟[[皇家马德里足球俱乐部|皇家马德里]]至2018年转会至[[意大利足球甲级联赛|意甲]]球队[[尤文图斯足球俱乐部|尤文图斯]]的近10年内，二人在世界上最受欢迎的比赛（同样也是观看人数最多的比赛之一）的[[西班牙国家德比|西班牙国家德比]]中每年至少对决两次。<ref>{{cite news |last=Badenhausen |first=Kurt |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/kurtbadenhausen/2014/05/16/lionel-messi-agrees-to-new-50-million-a-year-deal-with-barcelona/ |title=Lionel Messi Reaches $50 Million-A-Year Deal With Barcelona |date=2014-05-16 |access-date=2014-10-01 |work=[[福布斯|福布斯]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006091338/http://www.forbes.com/sites/kurtbadenhausen/2014/05/16/lionel-messi-agrees-to-new-50-million-a-year-deal-with-barcelona/ |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Cristiano Ronaldo: Juventus sign Real Madrid forward for £99.2m |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44785173 |access-date=2018-07-10 |agency=BBC |date=2018-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710154813/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44785173 |archive-date=2018-07-10}}</ref>在赛场之外，他们的运动用品制造商也不一样（[[阿迪达斯|阿迪达斯]]与梅西签约，[[耐克|耐克]]与C罗签约）。在他们的国家队，他们的赞助商与个人赞助商相同，[[阿迪达斯|阿迪达斯]]是[[阿根廷国家足球队|阿根廷国家队]]的赞助商，[[耐克|耐克]]也是[[葡萄牙国家足球队|葡萄牙国家队]]的赞助商；而在他们的所属俱乐部，情况则恰恰相反（[[阿迪达斯|阿迪达斯]]是[[皇家马德里足球俱乐部|皇马]]的赞助商，[[耐克|耐克]]是[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴萨]]的赞助商）<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/business/consumer/nike-vs-adidas-adds-faces-world-cup-sports-marketing-rivalry-n116371 |title=Nike vs Adidas Adds Faces to World Cup Sports Marketing Rivalry |date=28 May 2014 |access-date=1 October 2014 |work=NBC |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006115805/https://www.nbcnews.com/business/consumer/nike-vs-adidas-adds-faces-world-cup-sports-marketing-rivalry-n116371 |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Ricadela |first=Aaron |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-02/ronaldo-world-cup-ad-going-global-shows-web-trumping-tv.html |title=Ronaldo World Cup Ad Goes Global as Web Starts to Trump TV |date=2014-06-03 |access-date=2014-10-01 |work=[[彭博有限合伙企业|彭博]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140926141616/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-06-02/ronaldo-world-cup-ad-going-global-shows-web-trumping-tv.html |archive-date=2014-09-26}}</ref>二人同样也是足球领域中收入最高的两名球员，同样也是在体育明星中收入最高的球员之一，在薪水、附加条款、以及场外收入超过了一亿欧元。2018年，梅西在《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》运动员收入榜单上以1.11亿的收入上榜，C罗也以1.08亿的收入紧追不舍。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.usatoday.com/picture-gallery/sports/2018/06/06/forbes-top-10-highest-paid-athletes/35765295/ |title=Forbes' top 10 highest-paid athletes |work=[[今日美国|今日美国]] |date=2018-06-06 |access-date=2018-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181018003155/https://www.usatoday.com/picture-gallery/sports/2018/06/06/forbes-top-10-highest-paid-athletes/35765295/ |archive-date=2018-10-18}}</ref>2020年，二人拥有着体育人物中最多的社交媒体关注量，在[[Facebook|Facebook]]中拥有合计2.5亿的关注者。C罗是[[Facebook|Facebook]]上关注人数最多的人，拥有超过1.5亿关注者；而梅西则拥有第五多的[[Facebook|Facebook]]关注人数，他有超过1.03亿名关注者。截至2020年12月，二人在社交媒体[[Instagram|Instagram]]上的关注者总数为4.24亿，是Instagram上关注度最高的几个人之一。C罗是[[Instagram|Instagram]]上关注人数最多的人，拥有超过2.5亿粉丝；而梅西是[[Instagram|Instagram]]上关注人数第7多的账号，拥有1.74亿粉丝。在另一个社交媒体[[Twitter|Twitter]]上，C罗是关注次数第五高的人，他拥有超过9100万粉丝；而梅西则没有[[Twitter|Twitter]]帐户。<ref>[http://fanpagelist.com/category/top_users/view/list/sort/fans/page1 "Top 100 Facebook fan pages"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209081114/http://fanpagelist.com/category/top_users/view/list/sort/fans/page1 |date=2015-02-09 }}. Fan Page List.com. 检索于2015-01-29.</ref>

==对战历史==
在[[2007年金球奖|2007年]]的[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]{{NoteTag|一项由体育记者投票评选的奖项，以评选出年度世界最佳球员|name=金球奖}}评选中，梅西与C罗双双不敌[[AC米兰|AC米兰]]球星[[卡卡|卡卡]]，未能获奖。二人在[[2007年国际足联世界足球先生|2007年]]的[[国际足联世界足球先生|世界足球先生]]{{NoteTag|一项由国家队队长以及教练员评选的奖项，以决出年度世界最佳球员|name=世界足球先生}}评选中同样输给[[卡卡|卡卡]]。在那年的一次采访中，梅西表示：“C罗是一位非凡的球员，与他同在一支球队将是一件很棒的事情。”<ref>{{cite news |last=Brown |first=Lucas |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11667/2406670/messi-full-of-praise-for-ronaldo |title=Messi full of praise for Ronaldo |date=2007-02-28 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[天空体育|天空体育]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006074348/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11667/2406670/messi-full-of-praise-for-ronaldo |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.worldsoccer.com/news/messi-keen-to-team-up-with-ronaldo |title=Messi keen to team up with Ronaldo |date=2007-02-27 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[世界足球|世界足球]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006144249/http://www.worldsoccer.com/news/messi-keen-to-team-up-with-ronaldo |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>

二人的首次交手发生在[[2007–08年欧洲冠军联赛|2007–08年欧冠联赛]]的半决赛中，C罗当时效力于[[曼彻斯特联|曼彻斯特联]]，而梅西则效力于[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]，比赛过后，二人立即成为了主要的竞争对手。<ref>{{cite news |last=Garside |first=Kevin |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/columnists/kevingarside/2298101/Ronaldo-v-Messi-Gifted-duo-who-share-a-path.html |title=Ronaldo v Messi: Gifted duo who share a path |date=2008-04-23 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006102143/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/columnists/kevingarside/2298101/Ronaldo-v-Messi-Gifted-duo-who-share-a-path.html |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2008/apr/23/manchesterunited.barcelona1 |title=Is Cristiano Ronaldo a better player than Lionel Messi? |date=2008-04-23 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006071749/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2008/apr/23/manchesterunited.barcelona1 |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Marcus |first=Jeffrey |url=http://goal.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/04/23/ronaldo-messi-and-20-other-guys/ |title=Ronaldo, Messi and 20 Other Guys |date=2008-04-23 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006154438/http://goal.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/04/23/ronaldo-messi-and-20-other-guys/ |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>C罗在首回合中罚丢了一粒点球，<ref>{{cite news |last=McCarra |first=Kevin |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2008/apr/24/championsleague.barcelona |title=Ronaldo fluffs penalty but United hold firm |date=2008-04-24|access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009011403/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2008/apr/24/championsleague.barcelona |archive-date=2014-10-09}}</ref>但在次回合中，[[曼彻斯特联|曼联]]依靠着[[保罗·斯科尔斯|斯科尔斯]]的世界波，以1-0的总比分进入了[[2008年欧洲冠军联赛决赛|决赛]]，并最终捧起了冠军奖杯。<ref>{{cite news |last=Rutledge |first=Lewis |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/102148/report |title=Scholes seals final spot |date=2008-04-29 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[天空体育|天空体育]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083710/http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/102148/report |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>在年底的时候，C罗最终夺得了个人的第一座[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]，而他也表示他会再次获得该奖项。<ref>{{cite news |last=Roughley |first=Gregg |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2008/dec/02/ronaldo-manchesterunited |title=Ronaldo beats off Messi and Torres to scoop Ballon d'Or |date=2008-12-02 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006221218/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2008/dec/02/ronaldo-manchesterunited |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Norrish |first=Mike |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/3541051/Manchester-Uniteds-Cristiano-Ronaldo-wins-Ballon-dOr-and-says-best-is-yet-to-come-Football.html |title=Manchester United's Cristiano Ronaldo wins Ballon d'Or and says best is yet to come |date=2008-12-02 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007201723/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/3541051/Manchester-Uniteds-Cristiano-Ronaldo-wins-Ballon-dOr-and-says-best-is-yet-to-come-Football.html |archive-date=2014-10-07}}</ref>

