web/20141006101307/http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11661/5345883/ronaldo-im-still-no1 |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>而梅西的队友[[哈维|哈维]]则站在了自己的队友的边上。<ref>{{cite news |last=Lowe |first=Sid |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/may/26/lionel-messi-cristiano-ronaldo-champions-league |title=Cristiano Ronaldo is not in the same league as Lionel Messi, says Xavi |date=2009-05-26 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006165614/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/may/26/lionel-messi-cristiano-ronaldo-champions-league |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>而[[曼彻斯特联|曼联]]主帅[[亚历克斯·弗格森|亚历克斯·弗格森]]则直接称赞两名球员都已经跻身世界最佳足球运动员之列。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/fergie-ronaldo-and-messi-top-class-919957 |title=Fergie: Ronaldo and Messi top class |date=2009-05-19 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=曼彻斯特晚报 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006090035/http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/fergie-ronaldo-and-messi-top-class-919957 |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Ogden |first=Mark |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/manchester-united/5382023/Sir-Alex-Ferguson-cannot-separate-Cristiano-Ronaldo-and-Lionel-Messi.html |title=Sir Alex Ferguson cannot separate Cristiano Ronaldo and Lionel Messi |date=2009-05-25 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007145018/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/manchester-united/5382023/Sir-Alex-Ferguson-cannot-separate-Cristiano-Ronaldo-and-Lionel-Messi.html |archive-date=2014-10-07}}</ref>梅西在这场比赛中扮演了他并不习惯的核心角色<ref>{{cite news |last=Mole |first=Giles |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/manchester-united/5398147/Manchester-United-v-Barcelona-Lionel-Messi-centre-of-attention-in-Rome.html |title=Manchester United v Barcelona: Lionel Messi centre of attention in Rome |date=2009-05-28 |access-date=2014-11-20 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202132603/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/teams/manchester-united/5398147/Manchester-United-v-Barcelona-Lionel-Messi-centre-of-attention-in-Rome.html |archive-date=2014-12-02}}</ref>，并在第70分钟打进了球队的第二粒进球，这粒头球也帮助[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴萨]]2-0取得胜利，捧起了[[欧洲冠军联赛|欧冠]]冠军奖杯。<ref>{{cite news |last=Hayward |first=Paul |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/may/27/manchester-united-barcelona-champions-league |title=As gladiators clash, Messi is the champion |date=2009-05-27 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009040044/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/may/27/manchester-united-barcelona-champions-league |archive-date=2014-10-09}}</ref>同时，C罗在比赛的大部分时间里都表现出了柔和的态度，尽管他在比赛早期有一些得分机会，但当他被[[卡莱斯·普约尔|卡莱斯·普约尔]]牢牢防住的时候，他逐渐展现出了他的急躁与沮丧，最终也输给了梅西与[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]，只能眼睁睁的看着对手捧起冠军奖杯。<ref>{{cite news |last=Williams |first=Richard |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/may/27/lionel-messi-cristiano-ronaldo-champions-league-final |title=Cristiano Ronaldo in a mess as Lionel Messi takes lead role on grand stage |date=2009-05-27 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141009050713/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2009/may/27/lionel-messi-cristiano-ronaldo-champions-league-final |archive-date=2014-10-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/5399539/Manchester-United-v-Barcelona-Cristiano-Ronaldo-clockwatch.html |title=Manchester United v Barcelona: Cristiano Ronaldo clockwatch |date=2009-05-28 |access-date=2014-11-20 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202132557/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/5399539/Manchester-United-v-Barcelona-Cristiano-Ronaldo-clockwatch.html |archive-date=2014-12-02}}</ref>

从2009年至2018年间，二人每个赛季都在[[西班牙足球甲级联赛|联赛]]中的[[西班牙国家德比|国家德比]]里至少面对对方两次，也在[[西班牙国王杯|国王杯]]、[[西班牙超级杯|西班牙超级杯]]、以及2011年的两回合[[欧洲冠军联赛|欧冠]]半决赛中相遇。梅西在2009至2012年连续获得了4座[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]，并在2015年获得了个人的第五座[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]。而C罗则在2008、2013、2014、2016、2017年夺得了5座[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]，与梅西打平。2019年，梅西以7分的领先优势力压荷兰[[后卫_(足球)|后卫]][[维吉尔·范戴克|维吉尔·范戴克]]以及C罗，夺得了个人的第六座[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]也重新夺回了[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]奖杯数的领先优势。2021年，梅西奪得個人第七座[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]，創下世界紀錄，並擴大領先優勢。梅西和C罗各登上领奖台十二次，创下了记录。梅西合计夺得了4座[[欧洲冠军联赛|欧冠]]奖杯，而C罗也在效力[[皇家马德里|皇马]]的时候在2014至2018年的5年内4夺[[欧洲冠军联赛|欧冠]]，其中更是随队创下了[[欧洲冠军联赛|欧冠]]改制后首次获得三连冠的伟业。二人在夺冠之路上都发挥了巨大的作用。梅西再此期间也赢得了5座{{le|皮奇奇奖|Pichichi Trophy|西甲金靴奖}}与[[欧洲金靴奖|欧洲金靴奖]]（2010、2012、2013、2017、以及2018），而C罗也各三次赢得这些奖项（2011、2014、2015）。从2009至2018年，C罗曾连续6次蝉联欧冠最佳射手，而梅西则夺得4次欧冠金靴（包括2015年二人均夺得欧冠射手王）

==梅西与C罗之间的关系==
在2015年的一次采访中，C罗对他与梅西的竞争评论道：“我认为我们有时会在竞争中互相推动，这就是这场对决如此激烈的原因”。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Montague |first1=James |last2=Pinto |first2=Pedro |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/05/17/sport/football/football-champions-league-ronaldo-interview/ |title=Cristiano Ronaldo: I'm better than Messi |date=2012-05-29 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=CNN |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006125456/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/05/17/sport/football/football-champions-league-ronaldo-interview/ |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>C罗在[[曼彻斯特联|曼联]]时的恩师[[亚历克斯·弗格森|亚历克斯·弗格森]]认为：“我认为他们彼此之间的竞争不会打扰他们。我觉得他们在想成为最好的方面有自己的个人自豪感”。<ref>{{cite news |last=Palmer |first=Kevin |url=http://www.espnfc.com/story/1271003/alex-ferguson-cristiano-ronaldo-and-lionel-messi-both-the-best |title=Fergie: Ronaldo and Messi are equals |date=2012-12-20 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=ESPN |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006074354/http://www.espnfc.com/story/1271003/alex-ferguson-cristiano-ronaldo-and-lionel-messi-both-the-best |archive-date=2014-10-06}}</ref>梅西否认了任何关于他与C罗之间的竞争，并谴责了制造这种竞争的媒体：“只有媒体与新闻工作者想要让我们二人顶牛，但我从来没有与克里斯蒂亚诺（C罗）抗争过的想法。”<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/9478241/Barcelonas-Lionel-Messi-blames-media-for-inventing-rivalry-with-Real-Madrids-Cristiano-Ronaldo.html |title=Barcelona's Lionel Messi blames media for inventing rivalry with Real Madrid's Cristiano Ronaldo |date=2012-08-15 |access-date=2014-09-30 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007221041/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/9478241/Barcelonas-Lionel-Messi-blames-media-for-inventing-rivalry-with-Real-Madrids-Cristiano-Ronaldo.html |archive-date=2014-10-07}}</ref>

梅西在接受采访时说，他和C罗之间并没有紧张的关系，他们关系不合是假的新闻。

但是，据广泛的争论和记载中，两人之间存在着一种紧张的气氛。西班牙足球记者{{le|吉伦·巴拉圭|Guillem Balagué}}声称C罗在他的阿根廷同行背后称其为“混蛋”。<ref>{{cite web |last=Haisley |first=Billy |url=https://deadspin.com/book-ronaldo-refers-to-messi-as-motherfucker-behind-1657437792 |title=Book: Ronaldo Refers To Messi As "Motherfucker" Behind His Back |date=2014-11-11 |access-date=2018-07-15 |work=Deadspin |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715235801/https://deadspin.com/book-ronaldo-refers-to-messi-as-motherfucker-behind-1657437792 |archive-date=2018-07-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Balagué |first=Guillem |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/01/29/revealed-cristiano-ronaldos-obscene-nickname-for-lionel-messi-in/ |title=Revealed: Cristiano Ronaldo's obscene nickname for Lionel Messi in the Real Madrid dressing room |date=2014-11-11 |access-date=2018-07-15 |newspaper=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716075512/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/01/29/revealed-cristiano-ronaldos-obscene-nickname-for-lionel-messi-in/ |archive-date=2018-07-16}}</ref>卢卡·卡约里也在他的书籍《C罗：对完美的痴迷》中写到，根据他获得的信息，C罗在观看梅西踢球的时候会升温。<ref>{{cite web |last=Caioli |first=Luca |url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/4240/ronaldo-the-obsession-for-perfection/2012/04/20/3044935/messi-is-like-kryptonite-to-cristiano-ronaldos-superman-the |title=Messi is like Kryptonite to Cristiano Ronaldo's Superman: The story behind football's greatest modern rivalry |access-date=2018-07-15 |work=[[Goal.com|进球网]] |quote=Real Madrid insiders say that seeing Cristiano Ronaldo in front of the TV watching Messi play is priceless. When his agent Jorge Mendes is watching with him, he tries to calm him down by saying that people don't understand anything about football, that the Barça No. 10 doesn’t deserve to be the best in the world. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715235724/http://www.goal.com/en/news/4240/ronaldo-the-obsession-for-perfection/2012/04/20/3044935/messi-is-like-kryptonite-to-cristiano-ronaldos-superman-the |archive-date=2018-07-15}}</ref>在回应他和梅西的个人关系不佳的说法时，C罗表示：“在足球界之外，我们没有关系，就像我们与许多其他球员没有任何关系一样”，C罗补充道，他希望在未来的几年中说到这一点时，二人可以一起开怀大笑：“我们需要以积极的态度来看待这种竞争，因为这是一件好事”。<ref>[http://www.marca.com/2014/08/28/en/football/real_madrid/1409211779.html ""Messi and I are colleagues, work friends"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141125062432/http://www.marca.com/2014/08/28/en/football/real_madrid/1409211779.html |date=2014-11-25 }}. [[马卡报|马卡报]]. 存档于2014-11-21</ref>2014年11月13日，C罗还扬言要对{{le|吉伦·巴拉圭|Guillem Balagué|巴拉圭}}的言论采取法律行动。<ref>{{cite web |last=Lezra |first=Gabe |url=https://www.managingmadrid.com/2014/11/13/7211817/cristiano-ronaldo-lawsuit-guillem-balague |title=Could Cristiano Ronaldo Win a Libel Suit Against Guillem Balague? |date=2014-11-13 |access-date=2018-07-15 |work=Managing Madrid |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180715235722/https://www.managingmadrid.com/2014/11/13/7211817/cristiano-ronaldo-lawsuit-guillem-balague |archive-date=2018-07-15}}</ref>

在C罗从[[皇家马德里|皇家马德里]]转会至[[意大利足球甲级联赛|意大利]]球队[[尤文图斯|尤文图斯]]后，梅西也承认了很想念这位老对手，他说：“我想念克里斯蒂亚诺（C罗）。虽然很难看到他赢得[[西甲|西甲]]奖杯了，但他给了这个联赛很多声望。”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goal.com/en/news/messi-miss-having-ronaldo-in-la-liga/9ssjstrxi3gm1qnox63dz8pmu |date=2019-03-29 |publisher=Goal.com |title=Messi:I miss having Ronaldo in La Liga |access-date=2019-04-01 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128071211/https://www.goal.com/en/news/messi-miss-having-ronaldo-in-la-liga/9ssjstrxi3gm1qnox63dz8pmu |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在2019年[[欧洲足联|欧足联]]年度最佳球员颁奖典礼上的采访中，C罗表示他希望“将来与梅西一起吃晚饭”，而梅西则回复道：“如果我收到了邀请的话，那为什么不呢。”<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49516474 |date=2019-08-30 |publisher=BBC |title=Cristiano Ronaldo, Lionel Messi, and Eric Cantona light up UEFA awards |access-date=2019-08-31 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127194524/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/49516474 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==奖项与记录==
在二人竞争的过程中，他们一直在颁奖典礼上占据主导地位，打破了俱乐部与国家队的许多进球记录，以及创造了很多了不起的壮举。<ref>{{cite news |last=Adamson |first=Mike |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2012/dec/10/lionel-messi-record-year-numbers |title=Lionel Messi's incredible recordbreaking year in numbers |date=2012-12-10 |access-date=2014-10-13 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010204929/http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2012/dec/10/lionel-messi-record-year-numbers |archive-date=2014-10-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Hyde |first=Marina |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2014/dec/10/cristiano-ronaldo-lionel-messi-ballon-d-or-miracle |title=Cristiano Ronaldo and Lionel Messi: tit-for-tat miracles getting ridiculous |date=2014-12-10 |access-date=2015-01-04 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107051938/http://www.theguardian.com/football/blog/2014/dec/10/cristiano-ronaldo-lionel-messi-ballon-d-or-miracle |archive-date=2015-01-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Harland |first=Nick |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/sep/25/cristiano-ronaldos-remarkable-real-madrid-goalscoring-record-in-full |title=Cristiano Ronaldo's remarkable Real Madrid goalscoring record in full |date=2014-12-08 |access-date=2015-01-04 |work=[[卫报|卫报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106151402/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2014/sep/25/cristiano-ronaldos-remarkable-real-madrid-goalscoring-record-in-full |archive-date=2015-01-06}}</ref>这种竞争本身是关于荣誉与战绩的比拼，而不是一种基于厌恶的竞争，<ref>{{cite news |last=Smith |first=Jim |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/11223007/Cristiano-Ronaldo-versus-Lionel-Messi-is-a-rivalry-to-write-history-rather-than-a-bitter-personal-feud.html |title=Cristiano Ronaldo versus Lionel Messi is a rivalry to write history rather than a bitter personal feud |date=2014-11-11 |access-date=2015-12-13 |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222083905/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/players/cristiano-ronaldo/11223007/Cristiano-Ronaldo-versus-Lionel-Messi-is-a-rivalry-to-write-history-rather-than-a-bitter-personal-feud.html |archive-date=2015-12-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.thenational.ae/sport/primera-liga/20151017/as-another-record-falls-ronaldo-and-messi-continue-to-drive-each-other-to-greater-heights |title=As another record falls, Ronaldo and Messi continue to drive each other to greater heights |date=2014-10-18 |access-date=2015-12-13 |work=[[国家报_(阿联)|国家报]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222165807/http://www.thenational.ae/sport/primera-liga/20151017/as-another-record-falls-ronaldo-and-messi-continue-to-drive-each-other-to-greater-heights |archive-date=2015-12-22}}</ref>但也有许多梅西与C罗球迷互相贬低对方以及对方球迷。

梅西目前是{{le|西班牙足球甲级联赛赛季最佳射手列表|List of La Liga top scorers|西甲历史射手王}}，并在赛事的历史中送出了最多的助攻。C罗则是西甲第二射手，并送出了第三多的助攻。<ref>{{cite web |title=All-time La Liga assists |url=https://www.sportskeeda.com/football/la-top-assists |publisher=Sportskeeda |access-date=2019-06-24 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127175138/https://www.sportskeeda.com/football/la-top-assists |dead-url=no }}</ref>C罗目前是[[欧洲冠军联赛|欧冠]]历史最佳射手，同样也是赛事历史最佳助攻王。而梅西在欧冠中的进球榜与助攻榜中则稍微低于C罗之下，均为历史第二。二人在进球榜与助攻榜中均远远高于身后的[[劳尔|劳尔]]与[[罗伯特·莱万多夫斯基|莱万多夫斯基]]等人。梅西在2014年11月超越了之前的纪录保持者[[劳尔|劳尔]]之后，两人在2015年后你追我赶，互相打破了彼此的纪录。<ref>{{cite web |title=Apoel Nic 0–4 Barcelona |publisher=BBC体育 |date=2015-11-25 |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/29363780 |access-date=2015-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716205055/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/29363780 |archive-date=2015-07-16}}</ref>C罗在2015-16赛季成为了第一个在欧冠小组赛中进球上双的球员，他在6场小组赛中创造了打进11粒进球的纪录。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-soccer-champions-mad-mal-ronaldo-free-idUKKBN0TR2OC20151208|title=Ronaldo sets goals record for Champions League group stage|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2015-12-08|access-date=2015-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210221213/http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-soccer-champions-mad-mal-ronaldo-free-idUKKBN0TR2OC20151208|archive-date=2015-12-10}}</ref>他们二人是欧冠历史上前两个同样也是唯二个打进超过100粒进球的球员。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=2244072.html|title=Lionel Messi and Cristiano Ronaldo goal for goal|publisher=UEFA|date=2018-04-11|access-date=2018-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180421163322/https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/news/newsid=2244072.html|archive-date=2018-04-21}}</ref>

自2008年起，梅西与C罗就统治了[[国际足联金球奖|金球奖]]与[[国际足联最佳男子球员奖|世界足球先生]]等奖项；自2014年起，他们又统治了[[欧洲最佳球员|欧洲最佳球员]]一奖。但是，在2018年，他们近十年的统治被C罗前队友[[卢卡·莫德里奇|卢卡·莫德里奇]]所终结，一些媒体认为梅罗时代将要结束。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/46432933|title=Ballon d'Or: Luka Modric ends dominance of Lionel Messi and Cristiano Ronaldo|work=BBC News|date=2018-12-03|access-date=2018-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203230951/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/46432933|archive-date=2018-12-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/12/03/sports/luka-modric-ballon-dor.html|title=Luka Modric Wins Ballon d'Or, Ending Decade of Ronaldo and Messi Triumphs|author=Andrew Das|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=2018-12-03|access-date=2018-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181204053852/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/12/03/sports/luka-modric-ballon-dor.html|archive-date=2018-12-04}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/luka-modric-ends-ballon-dor-era-of-lionel-messi-and-cristiano-ronaldo-l6cxw3hmb|title=Luka Modric ends Ballon d'Or era of Lionel Messi and Cristiano Ronaldo|author=Matt Hughes|work=[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]|date=2018-12-04|access-date=2018-12-04|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127193620/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/luka-modric-ends-ballon-dor-era-of-lionel-messi-and-cristiano-ronaldo-l6cxw3hmb|dead-url=no}}</ref>而在莫德里奇接受《[[法国足球_(杂志)|法国足球]]》杂志的采访时表示：“历史会记载一个克罗地亚球员代表他并不强大的祖国在C罗梅西这两个在另外一个级别的球员垄断了长达十年后赢得了金球奖。（我）没有有资格同他俩比较，他们是无与伦比的”。自2008年起，梅西赢得了7座金球奖，C罗也赢得了5座；<ref>{{cite news |title=Ballons d'Or winners list |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/12/07/ballon-dor-winners-list/ |work=[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]] |date=2017-04-02 |accessdate=2021-03-16 |archive-date=2017-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171121051322/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/12/07/ballon-dor-winners-list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>梅西赢得了6次世界足球先生，C罗赢得5次；梅西也赢得了6座[[欧洲金靴奖|欧洲金靴奖]]，而C罗赢得4次。<ref>{{cite web |first1=Sorin |last1=Arotaritei |first2=Roberto |last2=Di Maggio |first3=Karel |last3=Stokkermans |title=Golden Boot (Soulier d'Or) Awards |publisher=[[RSSSF|RSSSF]] |url=http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/gboot.html |access-date=2015-08-17 |archive-date=2019-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190905010939/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/gboot.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

C罗合计赢得了31座重要的奖杯，包括7座联赛冠军、5座欧冠冠军、并带领[[葡萄牙国家足球队|葡萄牙国家队]]在2016年捧起了他们的第一座[[欧洲杯|德劳内杯]]，以及在[[2018–19年欧洲国家联赛|2019年]]率领葡萄牙赢得的[[欧国联|欧国联]]冠军。C罗也赢得了4座超级杯、4座联赛杯、6座本土超级杯、2座[[欧洲超级杯|欧洲超级杯]]、以及4座[[国际足联俱乐部世界杯|世俱杯]]。

以[[巴塞罗那足球俱乐部|巴塞罗那]]球员的身份，梅西至今已经赢得了创队史记录的34座奖杯，包括10座[[西班牙足球甲级联赛|联赛]]冠军奖杯、4座欧冠奖杯、6座[[西班牙国王杯|国王杯]]、8座[[西班牙超级杯|本土超级杯]]、3座欧洲超级杯、以及3座世俱杯。在国家队层面，梅西为阿根廷国青队赢得了[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会男子足球比赛|2008年北京奥运会]]的金牌，并在此前帮助国青队赢得了[[2005年国际足联世界青年锦标赛|2005年]]的[[国际足联U-20世界杯|U-20世界杯]]（世青赛）冠军，他个人也获得了赛事金球奖以及赛事金靴奖。梅西获得了[[2021年美洲國家盃|巴西美洲杯]]的冠军和3次[[美洲杯|美洲杯]]亚军，也在[[2014年国际足联世界杯|2014年世界杯]]打进了决赛，但不敌[[德国国家足球队|德国]]，屈居亚军。梅西个人获得了一次世界杯金球奖（2014）。

